<p class="ql-align-justify">一直是游客们拍照打卡的圣地。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">秋高气爽之日，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">正是乘风引线之时，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>崇文塔外，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>与亲朋好友共同放飞风筝，</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>舞动美好愿景，寄情于广袤天空。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">观文塔·品国学，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">在古韵宝塔之下，</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">以中华雅韵浸润心灵。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">自带仙气的泾河花海</p>
